      <h1 style="color: white; font-size: 2.25rem; line-height: 1.2; margin: 0 0 16px; font-weight: 800;">How Much Does a Bail Bond Cost in Stillwater, Oklahoma?</h1>
      <p style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.85); font-size: 1.05rem; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px; max-width: 640px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;">A transparent guide to bail bond pricing, payment options, and what families should expect when bailing someone out of the Payne County Detention Center.</p>
      <div style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.7); font-size: 0.85rem; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; gap: 16px; flex-wrap: wrap;">
        <span>By Karri McBride</span>
        <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">|</span>
        <time datetime="2026-03-07">{formattedDate}</time>
        <span style="color: rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">|</span>
